<plot>This documentary treats film fans to a behind-the-scenes look at the making of Legion of the Dead, a German-made horror film set in a demon-infested California. Includes footage of the filming process, as well as interviews with members of the cast and crew, who give their insights into what it was like working together on this project, and the efforts it took to bring the film to completion.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?353736</url></doc>
